      <h1><span style="color: rgb(128,0,0)">Welcome to the Bancroft Public Library</span></h1>
<p><span style="font-size: small">The Bancroft Public Library, &ldquo;your doorway to discovery&rdquo;, serves our community with information, entertainment and learning opportunities through print, multi-media and electronic resources.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: small"><br />
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Saturday Children's Group</strong></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing">Every Saturday from 11:00 am to 12:00 pm, the Bancroft Public Library invites children to attend storybook time for crafts, stories and much more.<span style="font-size: large;"><br />
</span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0);"><strong>Adult Colouring</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The Bancroft Public Library is offering adult colouring every </span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Thursday 10:30 - 11:30 am.&nbsp; Bring your colouring pencils and join the fun.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0);"><strong>Canada Reads 2016 Winner</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><a href="http://www.bancroftpubliclibrary.ca/canada_reads.php">Read the Illegal, the 2016 Canada Reads winner</a>.</p>    </div>
